description:
Welcome to Third Street, where a lot of cats and dogs live! Tama goes missing, and his friends try to find him. A new dog moves in to the neighborhood, but he looks really tough. Meanwhile, the cats try to find their warm paradise.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Have You Seen My Tama? / Dog Meeting / Our Waiha
Uchi no Tama Shirimasenka? Inu Kaigi / Oretachi no Waiha
うちのタマ知りませんか? / 犬会議 / 俺たちのワイハ
